data.description: This is a must see! Delightful 3 BR & 2 full Bathroom ranch with a huge great room that open to eating area. Ceramic tile & with freshly refinished hardwood floors, new carpet along with fresh paint throughout the home! Spacious rooms w/ 23x19 Great Rm to relax or entertain in. All rooms have overhead lighting & tons of closet & pantry space. Huge Mud/Laundry Rm. 1-Car attached Garage w/ extra wide drive. Convenient to schools, nature center & town!
